{"tid":1635052,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[10.7重陽] 各區開始多人","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:13:44.000Z","uid":95138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c01e8a19012cb27bc6523a4573fcd300bf5d5d","tid":1635052,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e9dc6b474e136ad205cff43d3eab4e4a54e039","tid":1635052,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"565df4a61049cd7f70d30f4d810cdda738f9b738","tid":1635052,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"食飽飯準備出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e91f3545c1fef7b8a8b0ef16bbb4e4125d97c0","tid":1635052,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"5aad01d2efed27459ea52a841c2177c722dbbb5a","tid":1635052,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c5706ca974819ac253b263a439a0b24ee394d5","tid":1635052,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34c1974afe8f72f2c2ebfb7f